<section id="introduction" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="introduction">Introduction</h2>
<p>In this session, we’ll cover the fundamentals of Java programming and get started with writing our first Java programs.</p>
</section>
<section id="setup-and-installation" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="setup-and-installation">Setup and Installation</h2>
<p>To start working with Java, you need to install the JDK (Java Development Kit):</p>
<ol type="1">
<li>Download JDK from Oracle’s website</li>
<li>Install JDK on your system</li>
<li>Configure environment variables (JAVA_HOME, PATH)</li>
</ol>
</section>
